# GODL — Agent Skill (Solana Mainnet)

> **Chain:** Solana (mainnet-beta)
> **App:** https://godl.supply
> **Stream API:** https://stream.godl.dev
> **WebSocket:** wss://stream.godl.dev/stream
> **Objective:** Deploy SOL to a 5x5 grid in slot-based rounds. Entropy program picks a winning square. Winners split the pool. Earn SOL + GODL rewards. Stake GODL for yield.

