## WebSocket Protocol

**URL:** `wss://stream.godl.dev/stream`

**Message format:** Binary. First byte = discriminator, remaining bytes = MessagePack (BigInt64 mode).

| Discriminator | Type           | Description                |
| ------------- | -------------- | -------------------------- |
| 0             | RESET_EVENT    | Round settled with results |
| 1             | ROUND          | Grid state update          |
| 2             | MINER          | Miner account update       |
| 3             | WINNING_MINERS | Winners list               |
| 5             | BOARD          | Round boundaries           |
| 6             | SLOT_DATA      | Slot synchronization       |
| 7             | TREASURY       | Treasury state             |
| 8             | AUTOMATION     | Automation V1 update       |
| 10            | AUTOMATION_V2  | Automation V2 update       |
| 11            | SOL_MOTHERLODE | Jackpot amount             |
| 12            | POOL_MEMBER    | Pool membership update     |
| 13            | POOL_ROUND     | Pool round update          |

**Auto-subscribed topics on connect:**

- `board`, `round`, `slot`, `treasury`, `sol_motherlode`, `pool_round`, `reset`
- Per-user: `miner:{authority}`, `automation_v2:{authority}`, `pool_member:{authority}`

**Reconnection:** Max 10 attempts, 3-second intervals.

